      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Hemolysis sensitivity across five flow-speed combinations",
      "description": "Relative hemolysis index (RH) evaluated across all five nominated flow-speed combinations. All predicted RH values below 1.0 relative to predicate device. Rank ordering of operating conditions consistent with experimental trends. Aleatory uncertainty from blood sample lot variability discussed in the body of the assessment report but no structured UQ node is attached to this result."
    }
