    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed consistent with MRL 2 requirements. Validation results demonstrate CFD model adequacy for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions. Relative hemolysis index below 1.0 at all five operating points. Aleatory uncertainty from biological variability in hemolysis measurements acknowledged in assessment narrative. The credibility body of evidence is sufficient to support regulatory submission for Class II CPB device.",
